cff-version: 1.2.0
title: LLM-Based Automated Grading System
abstract: >-
  R and Python pipelines for automated grading of student assignments using
  large language models. Supports a mix of programming, open-ended statistics,
  and closed-ended questions. Produces per-question grades and feedback via
  the OpenAI Chat Completions API (Python) and Assistants v2 API (R).
